{"id":300,"date":"2024-11-25T08:38:06","date_gmt":"2024-11-25T08:38:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/?page_id=300"},"modified":"2025-04-14T11:02:46","modified_gmt":"2025-04-14T05:32:46","slug":"contact-us","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/contact-us\/","title":{"rendered":"Volunteer devotees &#8211; Contact Us"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong>Significance of vani seva\/service to divine instructions:<br><\/strong>This service is most required and demanding at this point of time, to convey the sweetness of the rarest spiritual treasure offered freely to all of us by Sri Caitanya Mahaprabhu, Sri Nityanada Prabhu &amp; the entire Gaudiya Vaishnava Sampradaya Acharays, which no other incarnation had not given in the past 4000 yugas (1000 catur yugas or one day of Brahma).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This sweetness of the goal, its rarity and the necessity to attain the goal is narrated by HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj in unlimited variety of ways with a unique flavor which is most attractive and most tasty in many many lectures.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, whoever engages in this service will not only get the blessings of HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj, also all of our previous acharyas and Sri Caitanya Mahaprabhu !<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How does this service add value to whoever is contributing for this and also others?<br><\/strong>This service will certainly intensify the sadhana of those who engage in this service, as one has to hear the messages again and again while doing the service, thereby it strengthens one&#8217;s relationship with Krsna, and one will be blissful always, as one is connected with the all attractive &amp; all blissful Sri Krsna in a more conscious way. Moreover hearing (sravanam) itself is a direct anga of bhakti and as we all know Parksit Maharaj even attained perfection by this one service.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>And this is the service that gives life to all other services one may do, since it enlightens the value of other services &#8211; whether it may be chanting\/deity worship\/preaching.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Not only that, the endeavor of the volunteer devotees who are involving in this service, are further going to strengthen others faith, intensify others sadhana and strengthen others relationship with Krsna and make them also blissful. So, ultimately the endeavors are going to please all Jivas, all of our acharyas and Sri Caitanya Mahaprabhu ! If this is attained, what else is required ?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How practical\/flexible it is to do this service ?<br><\/strong>Moreover, all these blessings and benedictions are possible, by just being in the same place, wherever the volunteer devotees may present physically in this world. The volunteer devotees can make their home holy, spiritualize themselves and their devices. This is the boon and flexibility of this service !<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>List of available services:<br><\/strong>Below are the multiple ways by which the volunteer devotees can engage their skills in the service of HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj&#8217;s instructions(vani).<br>1. Hearing the lectures and validating \/ proof reading the transcriptions (transcriptions are done).<br>2. Hearing the lectures \/ reading the transcriptions to extract the potential shorts content \/ quotes which are beneficial for the common people and to intensify the sadhana of devotees.<br>3. Extracting inspiring context \/ quotes from the Acharays books translated by HH Bhanu Swami Maharaj which are suitable for making shorts.<br>4. Making shorts \/ reels video from the lectures using video editing tools.<br>5. Translating the quotes \/ making the shorts video in other traditional and foreign languages &#8211; Tamil \/ Hindi \/ Telugu \/ Japanese \/ Russian etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Volunteer devotees can consider all the above points and if interested, kindly contact us in the below details.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Mail ID : <\/strong>hhbsm.mediaservice@gmail.com.<br><strong>Contact :<\/strong>  9940340226 (HG Premabhakti Mataji)<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Significance of vani seva\/service to divine instructions:This service is most required and demanding at this point of time, to convey the sweetness of the rarest spiritual treasure offered freely to all of us by Sri Caitanya Mahaprabhu, Sri Nityanada Prabhu &amp; the entire Gaudiya Vaishnava Sampradaya Acharays, which no other incarnation had not given in [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-300","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/300","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=300"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/300\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":326,"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/300\/revisions\/326"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/bhanuswamiarchives.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=300"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}